# User Rules

## Documentation and Reports

- **NEVER create markdown documentation files** (`.md` files) unless explicitly requested by the user
- Do not create summary reports, refactoring guides, API documentation, or any other markdown files automatically
- Only create documentation when the user explicitly asks for it
- Focus on code changes and implementation, not documentation generation

## Code Organization

- Prefer clean, well-organized code structure
- Use proper subdirectories and logical grouping
- Keep files focused and maintainable
- Use internal/external API distinctions (underscore prefix for internal)

